title: Naturopathic Consultation
about: Initial consultations are 75 minutes long and consist of a detailed intake, complaint oriented physical exam and any necessary lab requisitions.
about_more: From your initial appointment you can expect a treatment plan to get started, along with any forms or lab work that needs to be completed.

title: IV Therapy Consultation
about: Initial consultations are 15 minutes long and consist of a brief intake, review of systems, discussion of goals and addressing any risk factors.
about_more: From your initial appointment you can expect a requisition for lab work and tailored IV plan lab results and approve you for the IV therapy.

title: Massage Therapy
about: We offer 60 and 90 minute massage appointments.
about_more: Our practitioner will collaborate on which therapies are going to be the most beneficial for your specific needs, combining massage, NST and osteopathy along with some take home information to maintain their wellness.
